{"tid":2005993,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"民間清算師要大家幫手投訴警曱","createTime":"2020-05-07T13:00:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-07T20:01:01.000Z","uid":252031,"like":34,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"b4179c6a871fb47e35cbcb825fe51b4afc64ca1c","tid":2005993,"uid":252031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T13:00:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/104015014549026/posts/137551464528714/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F104015014549026%2Fposts%2F137551464528714%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=w9JnFmhD9tlFtzSpwKDBdTcZFjLth35g1vO%2BxS%2F2N%2Fg%3D&h=46b5dc7e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/104015014549026/posts/137551464528714/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n清算師團隊收到元朗區議員 @瑞華- 林進 希望代為轉發以下訊息，希望手足能夠幫忙。<br />\n<br />\n尋晚係天水圍商場看到有一位市民在意樂餐廳對開位置，突然被一名防暴警員衝上前用腳踢倒，從直播片段看到該名市民未有參與違法行為。<br />\n<br />\n清算師團隊呼籲如有市民目睹上述經過，認為該名警員執法上有不當地方，可以向相關部門作出投訴。<br />\n<br />\n以下為相關資料以及投訴信樣本作參考<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/915080692167681/posts/1156046441404437/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F915080692167681%2Fposts%2F1156046441404437%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=w9JnFmhD9tlFtzSpwKDBdTcZFjLth35g1vO%2BxS%2F2N%2Fg%3D&h=4163d9c3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/915080692167681/posts/1156046441404437/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n=== 我是投訴信 ===<br />\n<br />\nto: csbcomp@csb.gov.hk<br />\n<br />\n敬啟者：<br />\n<br />\n本人欲投訴5月6日晚上，警員於天水圍+woo商場涉嫌以不平等武力對待市民。<br />\n<br />\n日期時間：2020年5月6日晚上約9時39分<br />\n地點：天水圍＋woo商場地面層(G/F)近意樂餐廳對開位置<br />\n投訴內容：根據蘋果日報新聞片段可見，當晚警員第四度以599G條例進入商場執法期間，突然衝向一名於餐廳門外的中國藉男子，更以其右腳踢向該名人士。而片段清晰可見，該名警務人員並無配帶委任證件，只有藍色行動呼號為QRF-3 1/4。<br />\n<br />\n由於事態嚴重，本人要求警方透過索取商場cctv記錄、傳媒片段以及警方自行錄影片段作出深入調查，本人現要求有關部門立即跟進該名警員的紀律行為，並停止所有前線警員如此不當行為。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞片段：<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200507/7GAADC4NGOB54LRWKF65MEOVSI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200507%2F7GAADC4NGOB54LRWKF65MEOVSI%2F&d=w9JnFmhD9tlFtzSpwKDBdTcZFjLth35g1vO%2BxS%2F2N%2Fg%3D&h=0a5058ac\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200507%2F7GAADC4NGOB54LRWKF65MEOVSI%2F&h=bd2be904\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200507/7GAADC4NGOB54LRWKF65MEOVSI/</a><br />\n<br />\n你個名"},{"pid":"1afd565f7d220ae41c255fd16096375883b70e44","tid":2005993,"uid":252031,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T13:01:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bWmu63s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbWmu63s.jpg&h=25f2c539&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nDSE手足加油"},{"pid":"0abd3f254977f718db87041c2c05f865618b76aa","tid":2005993,"uid":252031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T13:02:05.000Z","msg":"612 721 831 101"},{"pid":"bf137137e1ed85909191579b3c9fd609083b87c1","tid":2005993,"uid":252031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T13:02:18.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"588669ffaaf8d22798064bb1acec5138f278319d","tid":2005993,"uid":252031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T13:02:29.000Z","msg":"你今日幫襯咗黃店未？"},{"pid":"15dbd8fa4b7fcdf86f883622e481ced3f3ff21d8","tid":2005993,"uid":252031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T13:02:51.000Z","msg":"黑警死全家"},{"pid":"c62febbb142b05740ac904d8b6f9663845df5393","tid":2005993,"uid":252031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T13:03:02.000Z","msg":"五大訴求 缺一不可"},{"pid":"4c18795d694f0179998e7cdf4468d183bb4239c2","tid":2005993,"uid":53837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T13:03:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64015f4dd511914d85cb4c433e164acb5c1e1fad","tid":2005993,"uid":252031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"